rows.label: fev04_130_125_msg0002
rows.name: So good to be on land again!

rows.label: fev04_130_125_msg0003
rows.name: It was a pretty long voyage.

rows.label: fev04_130_125_msg0004
rows.name:
This place seem more empty
than Hana expected though.

rows.label: fev04_130_125_msg0005
rows.name:
Most likely because this is a small port,
separate from the main city.

rows.label: fev04_130_125_msg0006
rows.name:
That must be it. So I suppose our next
task is to journey to the capital.

rows.label: fev04_130_125_msg0007
rows.name:
From what I heard in the ship, if we
just head out of the port to the right,
it should be a straight path there.

rows.label: fev04_130_125_msg0008
rows.name:
Not too far off, then. Still, this is our
first time in this country, so we'd better
keep our wits about us.

rows.label: fev04_130_125_msg0009
rows.name:
Agreed. It might be best to make
preparations before we head out.
